These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, tulip, marigold, dahlia
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, strawberry, blueberry, lemon
1. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Flower   | amaryllis | tulip | dahlia | marigold |
| Food        | grapefruit | strawberry   | lemon | blueberry    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, august, june, july
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, light-blue, azure, blood-red
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
3. the person who likes azure is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes black is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
6. the person who likes black is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | june | december  | august  | july |
| Color   | blood-red    | black | azure | light-blue    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, cricket, basketball, snowboarding
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, pall-mall, aristoff, bolivar
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | snowboarding | basketball | cricket    | skateboarding      |
| Cigar   | aristoff        | bolivar     | davidoff | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, amaryllis, lily, azalea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo, prince, siglo
1. the person who growsamaryllis is between the bongani-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower         | azalea | rose | amaryllis | lily |
| Cigar   | prince       | bongani   | tiparillo    | siglo  |

