.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, monopoly, bridge
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, spy, satire, adventure
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
5. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Game   | mah-jongg  | domino    | monopoly   | bridge       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | adventure | satire | spy |

