.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, cain, aristoff, ritmeester
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, subway, taxi
1. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar   | aristoff      | cain | ritmeester | bolivar |
| Transport   | taxi | helicopter     | jet-ski  | subway  |

