.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, entrepreneur, firefighter, mechanic
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, guinea-pig, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the mechanic is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the photographer##1
5. the mechanic is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Job   | photographer | mechanic | firefighter | entrepreneur    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | guinea-pig  | rabbit     | ferret |

