.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, photography, woodworking, board-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dannemann, tiparillo, game
1. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
3. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the game-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the dannemann-smoker is in an odd position##4
7. the dannemann-smoker is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the tiparillo-smoker##2
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Hobby   | photography | video-games      | board-games | woodworking |
| Cigar   | montecristo  | game | dannemann    | tiparillo            |

