.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, september, march, july
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, rock, electronic, punk
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the fan of folk is between the fan of rock and the person who's birthday is in march##2
4. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in march is the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Birthday   | july | september   | october | march |
| Music-Genre    | punk     | rock | folk     | electronic  |

