.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
City: rome, venice, nizza, berlin
House: craftsman, art-deco, gothic-revival, cape-cod
1. the person traveling to rome is the cape-cod house##1
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the cape-cod house is between the craftsman house and the person traveling to nizza##2
4. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
6. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| City      | venice       | nizza   | rome | berlin |
| House   | gothic-revival | art-deco | cape-cod        | craftsman    |

