.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, cabbage, pepper, onion
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, emerald, yellow, onion-polo
1. the person who likes chestnut is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person eating kale##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes onion-polo##1
4. the person who likes onion-polo is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Food   | kale   | onion   | cabbage      | pepper      |
| Color      | emerald | yellow | onion-polo | chestnut |

