2. the british is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the mexican and the british##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | photography | reading  | drawing  | traveling |
| Nationality   | thai  | british | canadian | mexican   |

