.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, disco, hip-hop, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, badminton, rugby, cycling
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | rock | soul | disco |
| Sport           | cycling     | swimming     | rugby   | badminton         |

