.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, milk, water
House: futuristic, cape-cod, townhouse, tower
1. the person drinking cola is between the futuristic house and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the tower house##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the tower house is in an odd position##4
6. the townhouse house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | water | lemonade         | cola   | milk |
| House   | townhouse    | cape-cod | tower | futuristic   |

