.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bongani, baccarat, vegafina
4 different pets are kept: fish, dog, turtle, snake
1. the owner of the snake is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the owner of the turtle is the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the owner of the dog is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
5. the tiparillo-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Cigar   | bongani | tiparillo | baccarat    | vegafina |
| Pet   | fish   | turtle  | snake | dog     |

