.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, climbing, weightlifting, skateboarding
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, corn, grapes, carrot
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
3. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
5. the person eating corn is between the person eating carrot and the person eating grapes##2
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Sport         | skateboarding   | weightlifting | snowboarding | climbing    |
| Food   | grapes | corn  | carrot     | zucchini |

