.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, rock, ambient
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cycling, soccer, badminton
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
3. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the fan of country##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is surfing is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | country    | rock       | disco |
| Sport       | cycling  | soccer | badminton | surfing  |

