House: cape-cod, townhouse, craftsman, ranch-style
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
4. the townhouse house is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Game   | whist | backgammon | mah-jongg  | domino |
| House     | cape-cod      | craftsman       | townhouse | ranch-style     |

