.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, light-blue, aquamarine, pink
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, august, september
1. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
3. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who likes brown and the person who's birthday is in february##2
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Color         | brown | aquamarine   | pink | light-blue |
| Birthday   | september          | november | february         | august  |

 